thamizhachi is a 1995 tamil drama film directed by s. asokan . the film features napoleon and ranjitha in lead roles , with revathi , goundamani , senthil , vijayakumar , mohan natarajan and srividya playing supporting roles . the film , produced by k. p. shanmugam sundaram , had musical score by deva and was released on 29 june 1995 . the film became a failure at the box office .